# Keeps the docs/collaboration/ inbox directory present in a fresh scaffold while
# it is empty. Per-person thread inboxes (docs/collaboration/<handle>.md) are
# created at runtime by the AI agent when a teammate first raises a thread — they
# are NOT shipped by the scaffold, so they never collide with a template-owned
# path. See docs/collaboration.md for the thread/turn protocol. Remove this
# .gitkeep once real inbox files land here.
